# 🏥 Hospital Management Analytics Platform | Snowflake Data Warehouse

## 📖 Overview

The Hospital Management Analytics Platform is an end-to-end Snowflake Data Warehouse solution designed to automate healthcare data ingestion, transformation, governance, and analytics.

The platform processes patient, appointment, and billing data from AWS S3, applies business validation rules, captures invalid records, and provides secure analytical insights through Dynamic Tables, Secure Views, RBAC, and Power BI dashboards.

---

## 🚀 Project Architecture

```mermaid
flowchart TD

A[AWS S3] --> B[External Stage]
B --> C[Snowpipe]
C --> D[RAW Layer]

D --> E[Streams]
E --> F[CORE Layer]

F --> G[Exception Tables]
F --> H[Dynamic Tables]

H --> I[Dimension Tables]
H --> J[Fact Tables]

I --> K[Analytics Views]
J --> K

K --> L[Secure Views]
L --> M[RBAC & Masking Policies]
M --> N[Power BI Dashboard]
```

---

## 🛠️ Tech Stack

| Category       | Technology             |
| -------------- | ---------------------- |
| Cloud Storage  | AWS S3                 |
| Data Warehouse | Snowflake              |
| Data Ingestion | Snowpipe               |
| CDC            | Streams                |
| Processing     | Tasks                  |
| Data Modeling  | Dynamic Tables         |
| Security       | RBAC, Masking Policies |
| Reporting      | Secure Views           |
| Visualization  | Power BI               |

